1. Nf3 d5 2. g3 Nf6 {[%mdl 32768]} 3. Bg2 e6 4. O-O Be7 5. d3 {With this move White delays the fight in the center and plays a reversed King's Indian Defence, thus the nomenclature 'King's Indian Attack'.} ({Instead} 5. c4 O-O {and now} 6. b3 {is the Neo-Catalan. 6.d4 is the main line of the Catalan. 6.Qc2 is a peculiar move. After 6...c5 White has nothing better than 7.d4 when we have reached the 6.Qc2 Catalan.}) 5... O-O ({I prefer this move order to} 5... c5 6. e4 $5 {intending Qe2, which can even be followed with e5 and c4!? If} dxe4 7. dxe4 Qxd1 8. Rxd1 Nxe4 9. Ne5 Nd6 10. Na3 {White has good compensation for the pawn. Now 6.d3 is by far the main move, but we'll also check some rare alternatives.}) 6. Nbd2 c5 ({There are alternatives, such as} 6... b6 {and Colovic's suggestion}) (6... Nc6 {, but we will stick with Black's main setup.}) 7. e4 Nc6 8. Re1 ({This is more accurate than} 8. e5 Nd7 9. Re1 Qc7 $1 {hitting the e5-pawn and forcing} 10. Qe2 b5 11. h4 a5 {which transposes to the line with 10.h4.}) 8... b5 ({Sometimes Black tries} 8... Qc7 {hoping to get White into the position mentioned on the last move, but} 9. c3 $5 {as given by Plichta, causes fresh problems. So we will stick to the main line.}) 9. a4 {This is generally played to try to get an improved version of the 9. exd5 line, but it only has real effect if we recapture with the pawn, which is not our intention.} b4 10. exd5 Nxd5 (10... exd5 {is again playable, but after} 11. d4 {Black has to accept an isolated d-pawn because} c4 {?} 12. Ne5 {is very strong. The threat of Ndxc4 is one difference.}) 11. Nc4 {Taking advantage of the new outpost, but Black is still comfortable.} (11. Ne4 Bb7 {could be compared to the 9.exd5 line. The insertion of a4 and ...b4 hardly helps White.}) 11... Bb7 {Black is fine and can develop normally. A good example of what Black is aiming for can be seen in the following game:} (11... h6 12. Re2 Nb6 {Trading off White's best piece.} 13. Nxb6 Qxb6 14. Rb1 b3 {and Black had a great position in Miroshnichenko-Sevian, Saint Louis 2018.}) *

