mmon than 16.Qc2, but it's of equivalent value. It does keep an eye on the a7-pawn, which explains Black's next move.} a5 {[%cal Ga8c8,Gd8e7] This secures the a-pawn and stabilizes the c5-knight. There are other moves, but this is the engine's top choice and it has done well in practice.} *

