 (13. b5 {is certainly best. We'll consider that next.}) 13... Be7 {[%csl Rb4] Taking aim at the b4-pawn.} 14. Rb1 axb4 15. axb4 b5 $5 {[%csl Rb4][%cal Gb8a6,Ge7d6,Gd8e7] Fixing the b4-pawn. Instead of going for ... Nd7-b6-c4, which would be met with a quick e3-e4, Black plans to lay siege to the b4-pawn with ...Na6, ...Bd6, and ...Qe7.} *

