o accept split pawns because} 11. Rxc3 $2 {runs into} b5 $17 {when White cannot capture en passant because of ...Bb4.}) 10... Nxf4 11. exf4 Bxc5 {[%csl Gc5,Gc8][%cal Gb8c6] Black was fine in Shankland-Meier, Dresden 2013, and the bishop pair is always nice to have in an endgame.} *

