erately exchanges queens.} Qxa4 11. Nxa4 Ne4 $1 {[%csl Re1][%cal Gb4c2] Threatening mate in one!} 12. e3 Nxd5 {[%cal Ge4c5] We will take on c5 next with an easy position.} *

