%csl Gc7,Gd6] An invasive move. White does not commit his rooks yet.} Rd8 {[%csl Gd6][%cal Gc8b7][%mdl 32768] We cover the d6-square and prepare ...Qb7.} ({Black held a couple of correspondence games with} 12... Qb7 13. Bd6 Ne4 {but it looks a little shaky to me.}) 13. Rac1 Qb7 14. a3 {[%csl Rb4]} Rac8 {[%cal Ga6b8,Ga7a6] Black has everything covered and he can 'fix' his knight with ...Nb8, which also prepares ...a6 to evict the b5-knight.} *

