e enemy camp and preparing to take the c-file.} 16. Qc4 {White wants to exchange queens and go after our knight.} Qxc4 17. Bxc4 {[%csl Rb3]} Nxd4 $1 {[%cal Gf8c8] We grab a pawn and then we will win back the piece with ...Rfc8.} 18. Z0 ({For example} 18. exd4 Rfc8 19. Bxb6 {(Or 19.Bxe6 Rxc7 )} axb6 {In both cases Black is well ahead in development and should easily win back the pawn.}) *

