5.} ({Fixing the queenside with the immediate} 12... b5 $5 {is also possible.}) 13. Qd3 b5 $5 {Black allows e3-e4 because} (13... f5 14. O-O b5 {lets White grab the initiative first with} 15. a4) 14. e4 Qb7 $132 {[%cal Ga7a5] Black is ready for ...a5.} 15. Z0 ({After} 15. d5 exd5 {White should just recapture on d5 , with equality. Instead 16.e5?! was a bit too ambitious. 16...Be7 17.Nd4 a5↑ and Black had seized the initiative in Caruana-Anand, Saint Louis 2019.}) *

