1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Be7 4. cxd5 exd5 {[%mdl 32768]} 5. Qc2 {[%cal Rc8f5]} ({This will transpose to either} 5. Bf4 {or}) (5. Nf3 {, but we have to be careful with our move order.}) 5... c6 ({After} 5... Nf6 6. Bg5 {we are out of our repertoire.}) 6. Bf4 {[%cal Rc8f5]} ({Or} 6. Nf3 Nf6 {and we are in the 5.Nf3 Nf6 lines.}) 6... Nf6 {And we have transposed to the 5.Bf4 c6 6.Qc2 Nf6 lines.} *

