ally suffering for lack of space.}) 12. Bg3 $2 {White forgot the en passant rule.} Qd7 $1 {[%csl Rg4] This hits the g4-pawn. White is already in big trouble.} 13. f3 f5 $17 {[%csl Rg4][%cal Ge8g8,Gg4f5,Gh6f5] Black has a big initiative for nothing.} *

