ucture, but here having the queen on d2 and the rooks connected is a small triumph for White, kind of like the informational 10...h6 line.}) 16. Qxd4 (16. Bxb7 Ra7 {does not change much. After} 17. Bg2 Nd7 18. Ne4 c5 {Rb1} 19. Qd1 {Rfxd1} Rb8 20. b3 Be7 21. e3 c4 22. bxc4 Rb1 23. Rxb1 Rc7 24. c5 Nxc5 25. Rc1 f5 26. Nxc5 Rxc5 {the game Aronian-So, Stavanger 2018 was soon drawn.}) 16... Bxd4 {We have transposed to 12.Qd1. [/variation/22775236/#/12/w]} *

