 idea in these lines.} 17. Ne4 Be5 $1 ({After} 17... Bxb2 18. Rab1 Be5 19. Rxb8 Qxb8 20. Qxc4 {we do not get the queen to the desired c6-square.}) 18. f4 f5 $1 {[%csl Rg1] It is White who has to be very accurate, as his king position is weaker.} *

