m for his pieces.} 18. Z0 ({For example} 18. exd4) ({if} 18. e4 $2 Nd7 $17 {intending ...Rb3, ...Ne5, and ... d3 is overwhelming. Bxd4} 19. Rd1 e5 {and I prefer Black.}) *

