h pressure.}) (16. Rfd1 e4 $132 {with play on the e-file, which shows why it's safest for White to go to e1.}) 16... e4 $132 {Black's play looks easy to me.} 17. Z0 ({White can't take the pawn:} 17. Nxe4 $2) ({or} 17. fxe4 $2 Bd7 {with the idea ...Ng4 wins for Black.}) {Nxe4 fxe4} 17... Qg6 18. Qxc4 Rfe8 {is just great for Black, despite the temporary two pawn deficit.} *

