he engine also likes the mysterious} 13... Re8 $5) 14. Qd2 {This showcases a little trick, but White is in a bad way no matter what.} (14. e5 Qd7 $17) (14. d5 Ne5 $17) 14... Ne5 $17 {[%cal Ge5d3] Black remains a pawn up with a good position.} *

