xe6 Bxb7 27. Rxa6 Rxa6 28. O-O Rxa2 {The position has finally settled down, and it's equal.}) (25. a4 Bd3 26. Re7 Qf6 27. Kf2 Qb2+ 28. Kg1 h5 $5 {and Black's initiative persists.}) *

