ypical Catalan position that he was hoping for.}) 10. Qd1 e5 $1 11. Nf3 Qxd5 12. Nc3 (12. Qxd5 Nfxd5 {transposes to 11.Nf3 [/variation/32251774/#/11/w] in the main line.}) 12... Qa5 {[%cal Gf8d8,Gc8e6,Gh7h6] With ...Rd8 and ...Be6 coming, this is easy for Black.} *

