d7 14. dxc5 Bxc5 15. Bxd5 Qxd5 16. Qxd5 exd5 {[%cal Gf8d8,Gf7f6,Gg8f7,Gf7e6] White has saddled us with an isolated pawn, but it's easily covered. We'll just play ...Rfd8 and bring our king to the center.} *

