here. Again, White's kingside demonstration has not brought him an attack; on the contrary his own king is not comfortable. Some possibilities:} 18. Z0 (18. dxc5 $6 {opens lines for Black.} Rfd8 19. Qe2 Nxc5 {with ...Nd3+ in the air.}) (18. Qe2 $6 cxd4 19. exd4 Nb4 $1 {with the idea of attacking c2. Again ...Nd3 is a possibility , as is ...Nd5. White has to worry about ...e3 too.}) (18. a3 cxd4 19. exd4 Nb4 $1 {is still possible. If} 20. axb4 $2 Qxb4+ {wins the bishop on b5.}) *

